{"tid":92356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被北京毒霧玩殘健康？小米副總裁 Hugo Barra 辭職回老家，告別小米！","createTime":"2017-01-23T13:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T02:10:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef043c30021c65a9f5909517f2d5d691566be48","tid":92356,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"相信不少網友都有留意到，雖然小米是一家中國公司，不過為了<span style=\"color: red;\">建立</span>國際形象，小米在 2013 年成功請到 Hugo Barra 加入，成為小米全球業務的副總裁。而任職大約 3 年半後，Hugo Barra 今日突然在 Facebook 專頁上宣佈，因身體健康問題，要退出小米，預計將會在 2 月回老家美國加洲矽谷。到底是甚麼原因，導致 Hugo Barra 身體健康出問題呢？唔通係在北京吸得毒霧太多？<br />\n<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2017-01/23/207450/prince1025_1_99320e2c68e0c854907103b44321b07b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-01%2F23%2F207450%2Fprince1025_1_99320e2c68e0c854907103b44321b07b.jpg&h=53e7a009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就在大約 1 小時前，Hugo Barra 突然在其 Facebook 專頁上，宣佈要退下小米全球副總裁一職，並感謝小米給予他一個機會，可以讓他走上一個國際的舞台。在 2013 年開始，Hugo Barra 接下了小米副總裁一職，並從矽谷搬到北京居住。可是後來他意識到，在近這幾年居住在北京這個環境，讓他付出了很大的代價，甚至影響到他的健康。就因為這樣，這是一個明確的警示，提醒他是時候要回家了。"},{"pid":"098516818e9771abab040fd21e1817a0c9e436f4","tid":92356,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2017-01/23/207450/prince1025_3_61aa24fc2a8c9027314d00142ce74791.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-01%2F23%2F207450%2Fprince1025_3_61aa24fc2a8c9027314d00142ce74791.png&h=fec6e02c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於 Hugo Barra 的離任，相信這將會是小米的一大損失。不知網友聽到這個消息，心中會有甚麼樣的想法呢？你會因為這樣，為小米感到可惜嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/207450/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4568%2F207450%2F1&d=iZ4i5QPyjiZkb3EFLGXVpgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=9b85165e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/207450/1</a>"},{"pid":"fed9491b372bfb5896da016b0cd5445fa57f58cb","tid":92356,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"咪又係山寨，走唔走有乜影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bf07fc96cdcc5b430db8d953a388c383f8adb1","tid":92356,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"咁快老左三年半"},{"pid":"d2f6bb45a8fe1fb410edb2b781fe249bd77668cd","tid":92356,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"我只想身體健康。。。"},{"pid":"9d5b6155e2b3519b0641fb95cc9e063d81fe19fa","tid":92356,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"日日儲periodic table, 少咁啲中國人勞性基因都頂唔順啦"},{"pid":"1159b04c909168293b99409e933dfd90dd6d40f2","tid":92356,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日儲periodic table, 少咁啲中國人<span style=\"color: red;\">奴</span>性基因都頂唔順啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8ecaafd00859271cd4a8342887a8b095890d88b1","tid":92356,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"有錢都無命享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88406ee9a16bcfd266b5f1e07442c81e5fe59f4","tid":92356,"uid":20609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"執番條命算啦。錢可以再揾"},{"pid":"35076192c05c204908ef98a4c704d6777f7cc619","tid":92356,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c2351427ee761532a0590764741a351f5347dc","tid":92356,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"做乜唔用返自己部空氣凈化機呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/cczMLBzg_F9lu5VrTN70fw--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD02MDk7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTcwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--/http://nevec-img.zenfs.com/prod/tw_ec05-7/9df738c2-0359-4803-bd9d-16b4b3bf253a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FcczMLBzg_F9lu5VrTN70fw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD02MDk7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTcwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fnevec-img.zenfs.com%2Fprod%2Ftw_ec05-7%2F9df738c2-0359-4803-bd9d-16b4b3bf253a.jpg&h=21b00b45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64c0a101258029aec805ab1f897b49611aeb2a12","tid":92356,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04866acc4aa2ecd328cf4d7b9aa0c56e1360d829","tid":92356,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWFC"},{"pid":"96903c875246f143c589a2a440f31bb8e62e860c","tid":92356,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜唔用返自己部空氣凈化機呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/cczMLBzg_F9lu5VrTN70fw--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD02MDk7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTcwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--/http://nevec-img.zenfs.com/prod/tw_ec05-7/9df738c2-0359-4803-bd9d-16b4b3bf253a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FcczMLBzg_F9lu5VrTN70fw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD02MDk7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTcwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fnevec-img.zenfs.com%2Fprod%2Ftw_ec05-7%2F9df738c2-0359-4803-bd9d-16b4b3bf253a.jpg&h=21b00b45&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n可想而知呢部野係垃圾"},{"pid":"b0ae634c22da629a62e10f8b8486057a900278bc","tid":92356,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"小米空氣淨化器 2被爆淨化數據造假，沒裝濾網也能過濾空氣？<br />\njanus janus 發表於 2015年12月14日 15:00 收藏此文<br />\n<br />\nTwitter<br />\nPlurk<br />\n<br />\nFc7b9d1d8cbad5c1d5024fefa6c58047 小米的空氣淨化器 2（即空氣清新機），在中國推出不到一個月，最近卻被中國的網友質疑這款空氣淨化器在App上所顯示的淨化效果數值可能作假，因為有一個網友使用了一段時間，發現自己竟然忘了拆裡頭空氣濾網的保護膜，理論上這樣空氣淨化器應該是沒有作用的，但是App上顯示的空氣數據卻已經被淨化？<br />\n<br />\n小米空氣淨化器 2宣稱採用了一體式 360&deg;桶形濾芯，三層淨化。初效濾網攔截例如毛髮、灰塵等大顆粒懸浮物。第二層日本東麗 H11 級高效篩檢程式，過濾 PM0.3-0.5 達 99.5% ，去除小至 0.3 微米的微小顆粒，還可阻擋致病細菌 。第三層為高品質活性炭，可高效吸附甲醛等有害物質，有效去除空氣中的異味。<br />\n<br />\n不過，再厲害的濾芯，如果你買來的時候，沒有把外面的保護膜除去的話，濾芯基本上應該是沒有作用的。"},{"pid":"b5f37a0669edde91dcf334313a0ee1fe71181a41","tid":92356,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為有一個網友使用了一段時間，發現自己竟然忘了拆裡頭空氣濾網的保護膜，理論上這樣空氣淨化器應該是沒有作用的，但是App上顯示的空氣數據卻已經被淨化？</span>"},{"pid":"4e68dc889fb7f5deabd2ef2b31357af8eef098b5","tid":92356,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"慢性毒藥"},{"pid":"3738e75b3b9549e2222095cbf06d536b66c1e7e6","tid":92356,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa346a2083028c37b2067dbeecc3eee97181f46","tid":92356,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201cc1ce5d7f3ca2ed2d5dd72328dae6509a5986","tid":92356,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23